{"tid":1592440,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"請不要忘記 831 太子站事故另一重要線索：「港鐵控制室錄音」","createTime":"2019-09-24T15:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T14:01:50.000Z","uid":226548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5e6ec8a2ecde49395d6bfbb0f5a9b7c010e916b2","tid":1592440,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:16:55.000Z","msg":"【文：港鐵職員】<br />\n<br />\n831 太子站內發生的市民嚴重受傷事故，真相仍然是一個迷。由於當晚警方長時間封鎖現場，所以大部份市民都關注當晚太子站內的 CCTV 錄影，希望透過翻看太子站內的CCTV，求出真相。但要更了解其真相，其實有另一處的錄影錄音同樣重要。這便是 8 月 31 晚至 9 月 1 日的港鐵控制室的錄影錄音。因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">列車臨時要延長停留在那個站或某班車不停某個站等改動，皆由控制室的人員決定</span></strong>，而並非列車車長。<br />\n<br />\n831事故的發生及前前後後期間，究竟港鐵控制室是由誰人在指揮和控制？對話內容是甚麼？極可能為「831事件的真相」提供重要的證據。<br />\n<br />\n如果<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港鐵控制室的錄影錄音只會保留 28 天</span></strong>，那麼這重要證據可能很快被消毀。<br />\n<br />\n（編按：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗西鐵事件，有媒體取得當晚車務控制中心、車長及車務職員的詳細對話錄音</span></strong>，揭露當時車長曾通知控制中心月台及車廂有打鬥，但控制中心仍指示車長繼續播出要求乘客離開車廂的廣播。至於 831 太子站事件，大眾焦點集中月台的閉路電視，較少討論港鐵控制室的錄音。）"},{"pid":"393b81aad38a429adb2b3a74f54f0ea441c07d36","tid":1592440,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:17:26.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/請不要忘記-831-太子站事故另一重要線索-港鐵控制室錄音/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AB%8B%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%BF%98%E8%A8%98-831-%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%B7%9A%E7%B4%A2-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%A4%E9%8C%84%E9%9F%B3%2F&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUsdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=c23bcb05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AB%8B%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%BF%98%E8%A8%98-831-%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%B7%9A%E7%B4%A2-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%A4%E9%8C%84%E9%9F%B3%2F&h=71d0ac28\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/請不要忘記-831-太子站事故另一重要線索-港鐵控制室錄音/</a>"},{"pid":"77c4a819575d71fc69a7d777c9719c5192923726","tid":1592440,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"80d44adf41daa3eebc617b22b7046e91a705fbbb","tid":1592440,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"［請幫推行動post］今星期四：和你塞 美心MX<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590453</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4KHbAX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4KHbAX.jpg&h=3211b048&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"512011df1e912622e3583ba3e470894f52a62427","tid":1592440,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8e09be655a109b2f5b2a74ac169572820260ef","tid":1592440,"uid":293340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:28:03.000Z","msg":"黨鐵車廂內的CCTV片有沒有？"},{"pid":"85eb3e3937e5239eb939277415a710c3fb1981ca","tid":1592440,"uid":93251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:19:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2db9956f985d738052bede95f4ec03139b5035fc","tid":1592440,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea648cf6e784fddceb21ba1de44ab6bda4472bf5","tid":1592440,"uid":188035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:55:08.000Z","msg":"Pu